msgid "Keyboard/Controller Navigation and Focus"
msgstr "Loingseoireacht agus Fócas Méarchláir/Rialaitheoir"

msgid ""
"It is a common requirement for a user interface to have full keyboard and "
"controller support for navigation and interaction. There are two main "
"reasons why this is beneficial for projects: improved accessibility (not "
"everyone can use mouse or touch controls for interactions), and getting your "
"project ready for :ref:`consoles <doc_consoles>` (or just for people who "
"prefer to game with a controller on PC)."
msgstr ""
"Is ceanglas coiteann é go mbeadh tacaíocht iomlán mhéarchláir agus rialtóra "
"le haghaidh loingseoireachta agus idirghníomhaithe ag comhéadan úsáideora. "
"Tá dhá phríomhchúis go bhfuil sé seo tairbheach do thionscadail: "
"inrochtaineacht fheabhsaithe (ní féidir le gach duine rialtáin luiche nó "
"tadhaill a úsáid le haghaidh idirghníomhaíochtaí), agus do thionscadal a "
"ullmhú le haghaidh :ref:`consoles <doc_consoles>` (nó do dhaoine ar fearr "
"leo cluiche le rialtóir ar ríomhaire)."

msgid ""
"Navigating between UI elements with keyboard or controller is done by "
"changing which node is actively selected. This is also called changing UI "
"focus. Every :ref:`Control <class_Control>` node in Godot is capable of "
"having focus. By default, some control nodes have the ability to "
"automatically grab focus reacting to built-in UI actions such as ``ui_up``, "
"``ui_down``, ``ui_focus_next``, etc. These actions can be seen in the "
"project settings in the input map and can be modified."
msgstr ""
"Déantar nascleanúint idir eilimintí Chomhéadain le méarchlár nó rialtóir trí "
"athrú a dhéanamh ar an nód a roghnaítear go gníomhach. Tugtar fócas "
"Chomhéadain atá ag athrú air seo freisin. Tá gach nód :ref:`Control "
"<class_Control>` in Godot in ann díriú. De réir réamhshocraithe, tá sé de "
"chumas ag roinnt nóid rialaithe fócas a fháil go huathoibríoch ag freagairt "
"do ghníomhartha UI ionsuite mar `` ui_up``, ``ui_down``, `` ui_focus_next``, "
"etc. Is féidir na gníomhartha seo a fheiceáil sa tionscadal socruithe sa "
"léarscáil ionchuir agus is féidir iad a mhodhnú."

msgid ""
"Because these actions are used for focus they should not be used for any "
"gameplay code."
msgstr ""
"Toisc go n-úsáidtear na gníomhartha seo le haghaidh fócas níor chóir iad a "
"úsáid le haghaidh aon chód gameplay."

msgid "Node settings"
msgstr "Socruithe nód"

msgid ""
"In addition to the built-in logic, you can define what is known as focus "
"neighbors for each individual control node. This allows to finely tune the "
"path the UI focus takes across the user interface of your project. The "
"settings for individual nodes can be found in the Inspector dock, under the "
"\"Focus\" category of the \"Control\" section."
msgstr ""
"Chomh maith leis an loighic ionsuite, is féidir leat a shainiú ar a dtugtar "
"comharsana fócas do gach nód rialaithe aonair. Ligeann sé seo an cosán a "
"thógann fócas an Chomhéadain ar fud comhéadan úsáideora do thionscadail a "
"thiúnadh Is féidir na socruithe do nóid aonair a fháil i nduga an Cigire, "
"faoin gcatagóir “Fócas” den chuid “Rialú”."

msgid ""
"Neighbor options are used to define nodes for 4-directional navigation, such "
"as using arrow keys or a D-pad on a controller. For example, the bottom "
"neighbor will be used when navigating down with the down arrow or by pushing "
"down on the D-pad. The \"Next\" and \"Previous\" options are used with the "
"focus shift button, such as :kbd:`Tab` on desktop operating systems."
msgstr ""
"Úsáidtear roghanna comharsana chun nóid a shainiú le haghaidh nascleanúint 4-"
"threorach, mar shampla eochracha saigheada nó D-pad a úsáid ar rialtóir. Mar "
"shampla, úsáidfear an comharsa bun agus tú ag nascleanúint síos leis an "
"saighead síos nó trí bhrú síos ar an D-pad. Úsáidtear na roghanna “Ar "
"Aghaidh” agus “Roimhe Seo” leis an gcnaipe aistrithe fócas, mar shampla:kbd: "
"`Tab` ar chórais oibriúcháin deisce."

msgid "A node can lose focus if it becomes hidden."
msgstr "Is féidir le nód fócas a chailleadh má éiríonn sé i bhfolach."

msgid ""
"The mode setting defines how a node can be focused. **All** means a node can "
"be focused by clicking on it with the mouse, or selecting it with a keyboard "
"or controller. **Click** means it can only be focused on by clicking on it. "
"Finally, **None** means it can't be focused at all. Different control nodes "
"have different default settings for this based on how they are typically "
"used, for example, :ref:`Label <class_Label>` nodes are set to \"None\" by "
"default, while :ref:`buttons <class_Button>` are set to \"All\"."
msgstr ""
"Sainmhíníonn an socrú mód conas is féidir nód a dhíriú. Ciallaíonn **Gach** "
"gur féidir nód a dhíriú trí chliceáil air leis an luch, nó é a roghnú le "
"méarchlár nó le rialtóir. Ciallaíonn **Cliceáil** nach féidir díriú air ach "
"trí chliceáil air. Ar deireadh, ciallaíonn **Dada** nach féidir é a dhíriú "
"ar chor ar bith. Tá socruithe réamhshocraithe difriúla ag nóid rialaithe "
"éagsúla dó seo bunaithe ar an gcaoi a n-úsáidtear go hiondúil iad, mar "
"shampla, :ref:`Lipéad <class_Label>` socraítear nóid go \"None\" de réir "
"réamhshocraithe, agus :ref:`cnaipí <class_Button>` iad socraithe go \"Gach\"."

msgid ""
"Make sure to properly configure your scenes for focus and navigation. If a "
"node has no focus neighbor configured, the engine will try to guess the next "
"control automatically. This may result in unintended behavior, especially in "
"a complex user interface that doesn't have well-defined vertical or "
"horizontal navigation flow."
msgstr ""
"Bí cinnte a chumrú i gceart do radhairc le haghaidh fócas agus nascleanúint. "
"Mura bhfuil comharsa fócasaithe ag nód, déanfaidh an t-inneall iarracht an "
"chéad rialú eile a thomhas go huathoibríoch. D’fhéadfadh iompar "
"neamhbheartaithe a bheith mar thoradh air seo, go háirithe i gcomhéadan "
"casta úsáideora nach bhfuil sreabhadh loingseoireachta ingearach nó "
"cothrománach dea-shainithe aige."

